ImplementedSecurityControls.AccessControl: The onlyOwner modifier is applied to functions requiring ownership.
ImplementedSecurityControls.MinimumDeposit: A minimum deposit amount is enforced in the Deposit function.

ExistingProtections.FallbackFunctionality: The fallback function triggers the Deposit function when Ether is sent to the contract.
ExistingProtections.UncheckedLowLevelCalls: Potential vulnerability due to unchecked low-level calls in WithdrawToken and WithdrawToHolder.
